===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}}, equivalent to {{term|yond|lang=en}} (from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ġeond}}) + {{term|-er|lang=en}}, as in {{term|hither|lang=en}}, {{term|thither|lang=en}}. Cognate with Dutch {{term|ginder||lang=nl}} ('over there').

===Adverb===
